description: What starts as a fun and relaxing day quickly turns into a heart-pounding experience when Sonic finds himself upside down in the water. With his lover, Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin by his side, the power of love and trust is put to the ultimate test. Dive into this heartfelt tale of bravery, love, and the bond between two lovers.
